title: $\eta$-carbide (Fe$_{3}$W$_{3}$C, $E9_{3}$) Structure
comments:
Experimentally, the (48f) site is a random mixture of composition W$_{2/3}$Fe$_{1/3}$.  We use W for this site in the pictures above. 
 In many compounds the carbon sites has vacancies, which accounts for the varying stoichiometries in the compounds list.
